name: Sam Nichols x Supreme 2011 T-shirt
description: Sam Nichols x Supreme 2011 (box logo rip-off) T-shirt. (Limited/Trial run of 10 shirts: 5 Medium, 5 Large) Printed with Iron-on Transfer on Gildan Ultra Cotton. *Product is endorsed by Sam Nichols himself. PRICE DOES NOT INCLUDE POSTAGE Notes: - To keep the price low as possible, Iron-on transfer is the chosen printing method rather than screen printing. This may lower print quality and durability but this is for a piece of genuine Sam Nichols merchandise. - It is advised that the garment is machine washed and ironed inside out to lower the chance of the print from peeling. If peeling does occur, simply place baking paper over the image and repress. - It is also advised that the garment isn't tumble dried or dry-cleaned as this will result in the image quality greatly deteriorating.
